5:
The request said we'd find the
monsters here, but there's no sign of
them.
8: We arrived late, for one thing.
10:
We'll begin our search in earnest
tomorrow morning.
15:
Who knows. If we're lucky, the smell
of this food will bring 'em right to us.
19:
Maybe we could set a trap? I'm sure
we could manage something
simple enough—
25:
...Wait, really? Did we actually lure
them in?
43:
Those juices! The smell of that fat!
This has gotta be DELICIOUS!
Ugh! No fair!
57:
I was hungry and I couldn't resist
that smell...
I'll, um, be on my way now...
63:
No, it's okay... Would you like to eat
with us?
74:
Even though you guys are here on
business, you treated me to dinner!
Thank you so much!
80:
What are you doing in this forest?
You aren't stranded here, are you?
84:
I'm out here for a bit of training!
Thought I'd try fasting a little.
89:
A weird thing to say with a mouthful
of food.
92:
Yeah, I failed my training this time.
Maybe next time!
97:
Did you fail because of us? Sorry,
Makani...
102:
No, no! Not at all! I was the one who
chose to eat, after all!
105:
Besides, training for me is kind of a
hobby anyway.
114:
Yup. I like training. Getting your body
and mind in shape is fun, you know?
Nothing beats that feeling of
accomplishment!
117: So I'm trying out all kinds of training!
121:
Also I'm, uh... a monk, too...
I have a divine duty to fulfill, so I
think training is the best thing I can
do with myself!
126:
I see. Are you with the Church of
Farlana?
130:
Oh, no. I'm more local! Adherents
are pretty much limited to the
villages around here.
135:
You mean to say that yours is a faith
native to this region?
139:
Basically. So I was pretty shocked
when I showed up in Palpebra for
the first time!
142:
The Church of Farlana's temple was
huge... I hope we can have a temple
that big someday, too!
146:
This meat! Oh-hoho... This is
DELICIOUS!
151: ...Not much of a monk, is she?
156:
Well, you know... Customs vary from
place to place...
159:
They sure do! I was never taught to
fuss over that kinda stuff.
167:
I still gotta show my gratitude for the
hospitality!
169:
Aren't these the monsters you were
looking for?
174:
Looks like the food lured them in
after all!
178:
There weren't supposed to be this
many! On your guard, everyone!
182:
Relax! You've also got more allies
than you expected, right?
192:
Of course! You can count on me! I
pack a punch, even though I'm still
in training!
198:
Thanks, Makani. You really made
things easier for us.
200:
But... Are you sure you don't want
your share of the reward?
204:
It's fine, it's fine! Helping out was just
my way of saying thanks for the
meal!
213:
Hmm... I don't need the money, but
there is actually something else I'm
after.
216:
Information, that is! If you ever find a
place that would be fun to train in,
let me know!
220: I see. If that's what you're looking for...
225:
We could bring you somewhere that
could open lots of doors for you.
236:
Don't tell anyone about this, but we
actually travel to all kinds of worlds...
